=======
showevs
=======

showevs is a sample application that uses the stmm-input-gtk-dm library.
It shows the events received by different event listeners and all the 
devices recognised by the device manager.
It also shows what happens when multiple windows and dialogs are opened.


Compile and run
---------------

mkdir build
cd build

cmake -D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug ..

make

./showevs


